00:17:29,339 --> 00:17:32,259
This place is adorable.

249
00:17:34,178 --> 00:17:37,806
I'm not leaving this bed
for the next 48 hours.

250
00:17:37,890 --> 00:17:39,558
You in?

251
00:17:40,976 --> 00:17:41,810
Oh, I'm in.

252
00:17:46,106 --> 00:17:48,609
I love you, you know?

253
00:18:26,313 --> 00:18:29,108
The spirit of the '90s is alive
in Greenwich.

254
00:18:29,191 --> 00:18:32,319
I can't wait to see that dress on you.
You have to try it on.

255
00:18:33,403 --> 00:18:35,489
So cold.
I think I'm gonna take a bath.

256
00:18:35,572 --> 00:18:39,618
Oh. Use the one in the master.
It has well-placed jets.

257
00:18:42,287 --> 00:18:44,623
- I like the claw-foot tub.
- Of course you do.

258
00:18:44,706 --> 00:18:47,543
Because you're classy.
Cocktail? I'll get you one.

259
00:19:34,173 --> 00:19:37,092
