a life this grand someday.

260
00:19:37,176 --> 00:19:38,510
God knows, you deserve it.

261
00:19:38,594 --> 00:19:40,596
Darling, I made you a Negroni.

262
00:19:40,679 --> 00:19:42,347
Minus the unwanted pressure

263
