from an obviously unstable,
obsessed person, of course.

264
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:51,815
My hatred for Peach
has practically become sentient.

265
00:19:51,899 --> 00:19:54,568
Now, take your time and relax, okay?

266
00:19:54,651 --> 00:19:56,320
I've got a surprise for you
when you get out.

267
00:19:56,403 --> 00:19:59,281
Oh, and don't forget to use
