269
00:20:24,556 --> 00:20:26,308
Look at that!

270
00:20:26,391 --> 00:20:29,645
How dare she
invade your privacy like that?

271
00:20:29,728 --> 00:20:32,940
It's perverse! God, I have to pee.

272
00:20:53,919 --> 00:20:55,671
I'll double back for that.

273
00:20:57,756 --> 00:21:01,009
Now, how long is she going to
stand there staring at you?

274
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:56,106
Hello?

275
00:21:57,816 --> 00:21:58,900
Anyone here?

276
00:22:05,157 --> 00:22:07,242
- Who is that?
- Um...

277
00:22:07,993 --> 00:22:09,494
It's the surprise.

278
00:22:12,247 --> 00:22:13,832
She has a gun, Beck.

279
00:22:14,458 --> 00:22:16,877
She's not in her right mind
and you know it.

280
00:22:17,919 --> 00:22:19,379
I have to do something.

281
00:22:20,005 --> 00:22:22,841
80% of gun accidents happen in the home.

282
00:22:29,556 --> 00:22:34,061
